title: Different views, different sizes, and different prices we have it all!
posting_body: ['IMT at City Park', '1600 Fillmore Street', 'Denver, CO 80206', 'show contact info', 'Unit Information:', '1 Bedroom | 1 Bath', 'Unit Size:', '804 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent:', '$1865', 'Lease Terms:', 'Variable', 'Property Description:', '**Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.', '**', 'Living at IMT at City Park will allow you to experience everything Denver has to offer!', 'Being at City Park the Denver Zoo, the Denver Museum of Nature and Science, as well as minutes from 17th street also known as Restaurant Row, IMT at City Park is located in the most highly desirable area of Denver.', 'Not to mention, Colorado Mills Outlet Mall, Coors Field, Mile High Stadium, and downtown Denver are also within a quick drive!', 'Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today!', '<URL>', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Call us today!', 'show contact info', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Pet Ownership Policy:', 'Pets allowed!', 'For one pet, pet fee (non-refundable) is $350 and pet rent is $35 per month.', 'For two pets, pet fee (non-refundable) is $500 and pet rent is $45 per month.', 'No weight restriction.', 'Some breed restrictions apply.', 'Proudly managed by IMT Residential', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '3596D02E305440']
